readme:
Service Usage

The service is used by consumers to send threat filter to the ICSE system.

Service Behviour

This service can be used in both Synconise and asyncronise modes. In syncronise modes the request will respond with a pending if the threat filter can not be returned until further conditional logic or human intervention is required. Events can then be subscribed using the UUID suuplied in this request to monitor futher updates.

Service Appology

No penguins were harmed in the making of this service but the same can not be said for the various dogs that have been involved.
